BrainTree,offers,online,merchants,a,payment,gateway,to,enable,the,processing,of,credit,card,payments,Additionally,merchants,are,offered,a,merchant,account,recurring,billing,and,credit,card,storage,The,Braintree,Gateway,API,can,be,used,two,ways,either,Server,to,Server,or,Transparent,Redirect,In,the,Server,to,Server,scenario,customers,submit,their,credit,card,data,on,the,developer,website,to,their,server,The,Transparent,Redirect,API,eliminates,the,handling,and,processing,of,credit,card,data,from,the,developer,s,environment